na has spent over 15 years in the title insurance industry as a Sr. Title Examiner and RE Paralegal. Having managed teams and being on all sides of the real estate transaction over two decades she brings extensive experience in title insurance, land title, underwriting and risk management. Christina is a Certified Paralegal, earning her degree from MacCormac College, Chicago, focusing on Real Estate Law. She has also earned both her Illinois Title Professional (ITP) and Illinois Escrow Professional (IEP) designation. Christina is an avid traveler and enjoys spending time with family and friends.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #2b449c;\">CP: MacCormac College</span>'),(5896,52,'_builder_0_team_sections_1_team_member_0_content','field_6387a70bfcf9c'),(5897,52,'builder_0_team_sections_1_team_member_1_headshot','361'),(5898,52,'_builder_0_team_sections_1_team_member_1_headshot','field_6387a8658d719'),(5899,52,'builder_0_team_sections_1_team_member_1_name','Shawn Gibbons'),(5900,52,'_builder_0_team_sections_1_team_member_1_name','field_6387a6fdfcf9a'),(5901,52,'builder_0_team_sections_1_team_member_1_title','Vice President of Acquisitions'),(5902,52,'_builder_0_team_sections_1_team_member_1_title','field_6387a703fcf9b'),(5903,52,'builder_0_team_sections_1_team_member_1_email','sgibbons@american-postal.com'),(5904,52,'_builder_0_team_sections_1_team_member_1_email','field_6387b71a49ea4'),(5905,52,'builder_0_team_sections_1_team_member_1_content','<span style=\"color: #2b449c;\">BS: North Central College</span>'),(5906,52,'_builder_0_team_sections_1_team_member_1_content','field_6387a70bfcf9c'),(5907,52,'builder_0_team_sections_1_team_member_2_headshot','360'),(5908,52,'_builder_0_team_sections_1_team_member_2_headshot','field_6387a8658d719'),(5909,52,'builder_0_team_sections_1_team_member_2_name','Brian Bamford'),(5910,52,'_builder_0_team_sections_1_team_member_2_name','field_6387a6fdfcf9a'),(5911,52,'builder_0_team_sections_1_team_member_2_title','Vice President of A