nal (ITP) and Illinois Escrow Professional (IEP) designation. Christina is an avid traveler and enjoys spending time with family and friends.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #2b449c;\">CP: MacCormac College</span>'),(8049,385,'_builder_0_team_sections_1_team_member_0_content','field_6387a70bfcf9c'),(8050,385,'builder_0_team_sections_1_team_member_1_headshot','361'),(8051,385,'_builder_0_team_sections_1_team_member_1_headshot','field_6387a8658d719'),(8052,385,'builder_0_team_sections_1_team_member_1_name','Shawn Gibbons'),(8053,385,'_builder_0_team_sections_1_team_member_1_name','field_6387a6fdfcf9a'),(8054,385,'builder_0_team_sections_1_team_member_1_title','Vice President of Acquisitions'),(8055,385,'_builder_0_team_sections_1_team_member_1_title','field_6387a703fcf9b'),(8056,385,'builder_0_team_sections_1_team_member_1_email','sgibbons@american-postal.com'),(8057,385,'_builder_0_team_sections_1_team_member_1_email','field_6387b71a49ea4'),(8058,385,'builder_0_team_sections_1_team_member_1_content','<span style=\"color: #2b449c;\">BS: North Central College</span>'),(8059,385,'_builder_0_team_sections_1_team_member_1_content','field_6387a70bfcf9c'),(8060,385,'builder_0_team_sections_1_team_member_2_headshot','360'),(8061,385,'_builder_0_team_sections_1_team_member_2_headshot','field_6387a8658d719'),(8062,385,'builder_0_team_sections_1_team_member_2_name','Brian Bamford'),(8063,385,'_builder_0_team_sections_1_team_member_2_name','field_6387a6fdfcf9a'),(8064,385,'builder_0_team_sections_1_team_member_2_title','Vice President of Acquisitions'),(8065,385,'_builder_0_team_sections_1_team_member_2_title','field_6387a703fcf9b'),(8066,385,'builder_0_team_sections_1_team_member_2_email','bbamford@american-postal.com'),(8067,385,'_builder_0_team_sections_1_team_member_2_email','field_6387b71a49ea4'),(8068,385,'builder_0_team_sections_1_team_member_2_content','BS: Business Management  Marian University'),(8069,385,'_builder_0_team_sections_1_team_member_2_content','field_638