8464'),(8683,389,'builder_0_content_classes',''),(8684,389,'_builder_0_content_classes','field_63866af6c8465'),(8685,389,'builder_0_content_content','<h2>What options does American Postal Infrastructure (API) offer to postal building owners?</h2>\r\nAPI offers 2 solutions for owners: 100% cash for your post office or participating in our Partner Up Program. Learn more HERE.\r\n\r\n[divider]\r\n<h2>How can I find out the value of my post office?</h2>\r\nCall us at (844)API-TEAM, email <a href=\"mailto:contact@american-postal.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">contact@american-postal.com</a>, or fill out our online inquiry form HERE.\r\n\r\n[divider]\r\n<h2>What determines the value of my post office?</h2>\r\nAnnual rent, building square feet, maintenance responsibility, tax responsibility, property condition, and age, among other factors.\r\n\r\n[divider]\r\n<h2>Im a current tenant of API. Who do I contact for maintenance-related? questions?</h2>\r\nFor maintenance-related questions, please email <a href=\"mailto:assetmanagement@american-postal.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">assetmanagement@american-postal.com</a> or call <a href=\"tel:+13017031007\">301-703-1007</a>.\r\n\r\n[divider]\r\n<h2>I own a unit in a multi-tenant site. Will API purchase my unit?</h2>\r\nOur core competency is owning individual stand-alone buildings, however, we do consider parceling off individual units from multi-tenant facilities. Please contact us at (844) API-TEAM.'),(8686,389,'_builder_0_content_content','field_63866abefadc5'),(8687,389,'builder_0_content',''),(8688,389,'_builder_0_content','field_63866abefadc2'),(8689,389,'builder','2'),(8690,389,'_builder','field_638641ce359a0'),(8691,389,'builder_1_layout','Content Section'),(8692,389,'_builder_1_layout','field_638641ce431be'),(8693,389,'builder_1_content_section_background_image','223'),(8694,389,'_builder_1_content_section_background_image','field_638641ce45904'),(8695,389,'builder_1_content_section_style','height:6