'field_638641ce431be'),(8725,390,'builder_1_content_section_background_image','174'),(8726,390,'_builder_1_content_section_background_image','field_638641ce45904'),(8727,390,'builder_1_content_section_style',''),(8728,390,'_builder_1_content_section_style','field_638641ce45907'),(8729,390,'builder_1_content_section_classes',''),(8730,390,'_builder_1_content_section_classes','field_638641ce4590a'),(8731,390,'builder_1_content_section_content','<h2 class=\"text-gray\">Our Vision for the Future PO</h2>\r\n<p class=\"text-white\" style=\"font-size: 135%;\">The United States Postal Service issued its 10-year plan in March of 2021 to achieve financial sustainability and service excellence. Our vision is in line with the 10-year plan, and we are preparing our postal properties to become the post offices of the future. As such, we are exploring enhancements to help revitalize postal properties such as: Solar power, electric vehicle charging stations, parcel pickup lockers, business services, on-site banking, community centers, remote learning, and telemedicine, to name a few. Our vision and dedicated resources will help deliver the post office of the future today!</p>'),(8732,390,'_builder_1_content_section_content','field_638641ce4590d'),(8733,390,'builder_1_content_section_image',''),(8734,390,'_builder_1_content_section_image','field_638641ce4590f'),(8735,390,'builder_1_content_section',''),(8736,390,'_builder_1_content_section','field_638641ce431c1'),(8737,390,'builder_2_layout','Content Section'),(8738,390,'_builder_2_layout','field_638641ce431be'),(8739,390,'builder_2_content_section_background_image',''),(8740,390,'_builder_2_content_section_background_image','field_638641ce45904'),(8741,390,'builder_2_content_section_style',''),(8742,390,'_builder_2_content_section_style','field_638641ce45907'),(8743,390,'builder_2_content_section_classes',''),(8744,390,'_builder_2_content_section_classes','field_638641ce4590a'),(8745,390,'builder_2_content_section_content','<h2 class=\"\"><strong>American Postal Infrastructure</strong></h2>\r\nis a trusted and preferred manager, owner, and buyer of postal properties.'),(8746,390,'_builder_2_content_section_content','field_638641ce4590d'),(8747,390,'builder_2_content_section_image','175'),(8748,390,'_builder_2_content_section_image','field_638641ce4590f'),(8749,390,'builder_2_content_section',''),(8750,390,'_builder_2_content_section','field_638641ce431c1'),(8751,390,'builder_3_layout','Content Section'),(8752,390,'_builder_3_layout','field_638641ce431be'),(8753,390,'builder_3_content_section_background_image','176'),(8754,390,'_builder_3_content_section_background_image','field_638641ce45904'),(8755,390,'builder_3_content_section_style','background-position: right;'),(8756,390,'_builder_3_content_section_style','field_638641ce45907'),(8757,390,'builder_3_content_section_classes',''),(8758,390,'_builder_3_content_section_classes','field_638641ce4590a'),(8759,390,'builder_3_content_section_content','[button href=\"#\" class=\"btn-main\" style=\"\"]MEET OUR TEAM[/button]\r\n<div class=\"\" style=\"height: 100px;\"></div>\r\n[button href=\"#\" class=\"btn-main\" style=\"\"]WORK AT API[/button]'),(8760,390,'_builder_3_content_section_content','field_638641ce4590d'),(8761,390,'builder_3_content_section_image',''),(8762,390,'_builder_3_content_section_image','field_638641ce4590f'),(8763,390,'builder_3_content_section',''),(8764,390,'_builder_3_content_section','field_638641ce431c1'),(8765,391,'custom_css',''),(8766,391,'_custom_css','field_605cafca65108'),(8767,391,'builder_0_layout','Content & Testimonials'),(8768,391,'_builder_0_layout','field_638641ce431be'),(8769,391,'builder_0_content_testimonials_background_image',''),(8770,391,'_builder_0_content_testimonials_background_image','field_638659b1051bd'),(8771,391,'builder_0_content_testimonials_content','<h2 class=\"text-accent-secondary\">Not ready to sell?</h2>\r\n<h3 class=\"text-accent-secondary\">Explore an equity partnership with API</h3>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2>OWNER CHALLENGE</h2>\r\nLongtime owners of post office property likely have a substantial tax liability as a result of a large difference between their tax basis and the market value of the property.\r\n\r\nWith our Partner Up Program, postal owners have an opportunity to partner shoulder to shoulder with our investors, including individuals, universities, endowments, pension funds, and other investors, all in a potentially tax-advantaged structure.\r\n\r\n[divider]\r\n<h2>AMERICAN POSTAL SOLUTION</h2>\r\nBy participating in our Partner Up Program, post office property owners elect to contribute their property to our pool of over 625 properties in exchange for shares, which provide a number of near-term and long-term benefits:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Deferral of taxes</li>\r\n 	<li>Cash flow from a much larger and more diversified portfolio, at a level that can exceed current cash flow from the property</li>\r\n 	<li>Quarterly cash distributions</li>\r\n 	<li>Elimination of requirement for day-to-day property management</li>\r\n 	<li>Options for liquidity</li>\r\n 	<li>Potential estate planning benefits</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<em class=\"small\">* Speak to your tax professional to get tax implications for your property.</em>\r\n\r\n[divider]\r\n<h2>CONTINUE TO SUPPORT THE USPS</h2>\r\nBy participating in our Partner Up Program, you have the opportunity to remain engaged in the USPS community as a continued investor and supporter.\r\n\r\nIn addition, participants in our Partner Up Program have the option to join our Owners Council, where you can advise our company and continue interacting with other postal property owners.\r\n<div>\r\n<div>[button href=\"#\" class=\"btn-main\" style=\"\"]CONTACT INVESTOR RELATIONS[/button]</div>\r\n</div>'),(8772,391,'_builder_0_content_testimonials_content','field_638657994221e'),(8773,391,'builder_0_content_testimonials_testimonials_0_content','Thank you for a wonderful experience. You personally renewed my belief that there are good and honest people in this world, who accomplish things through fair treatment of all parties. You do what you say and expect others to do the same. From the first telephone call, to those after closing, Mr. Shawn Gibbons was my contact person. Every verbal commitment he gave me was confirmed via email and carried out to the letter. It was a very pleasant and efficient experience. As we went through the closing process, the APIP staff were most helpful in sharing their experience and knowledge in helping us perform our requirements. Every person within their organization, including the inspectors, Title Company, and especially the closing agents, were honest, helpful, and efficient. As someone who has personally put over four million square feet of design-built construction in place and brokered deals with national companies, I can say with confidence that if everyone with whom I had to deal were like this company, I would come out of retirement and enjoy going back to work.'),(8774,391,'_builder_0_content_testimonials_testimonials_0_content','field_638657d242220'),(8775,391,'builder_0_content_testimonials_testimonials_0_name','Ron H., MN'),(8776,391,'_builder_0_content_testimonials_testimonials_0_name','field_638657dc42221'),(8777,391,'builder_0_content_testimonials_testimonials','1'),(8778,391,'_builder_0_content_testimonials_testimonials','field_638657bb4221f'),(8779,391,'builder_0_content_testimonials',''),(8780,391,'_builder_0_content_testimonials','field_6386577f4221d'),(8781,391,'builder','2'),(8782,391,'_builder','field_638641ce359a0'),(8783,391,'builder_1_layout','Content Section'),(8784,391,'_builder_1_layout','field_638641ce431be'),(8785,391,'builder_1_content_section_background_image','320'),(8786,391,'_builder_1_content_section_background_image','field_638641ce45904'),(8787,391,'builder_1_content_section_style','height:600px;'),(8788,391,'_builder_1_content_section_style','field_638641ce45907'),(8789,391,'builder_1_content_section_classes','img-emp