<h2>HOMES FOR OUR TROOPS</h2>\r\nHomes For Our Troops builds and donates specially adapted custom homes nationwide for severely injured post-9/11 Veterans, to enable them to rebuild their lives. Most of these Veterans have sustained injuries including multiple limb amputations, partial or full paralysis, and/or severe traumatic brain injury (TBI). These homes restore some of the freedom and independence our Veterans sacrificed while defending our country, and enable them to focus on their family, recovery, and rebuilding their lives.'),(8816,392,'_builder_0_thumbnail_icontent_sections_1_content','field_6387822bdd583'),(8817,392,'builder_0_thumbnail_icontent_sections_2_thumbnail','291'),(8818,392,'_builder_0_thumbnail_icontent_sections_2_thumbnail','field_63878221dd582'),(8819,392,'builder_0_thumbnail_icontent_sections_2_content','<h2>ST. JUDE CHILDRENS RESEARCH HOSPITAL</h2>\r\nThe mission of St. Jude Childrens Research Hospital is to advance cures, and means of prevention, for pediatric catastrophic diseases through research and treatment. Consistent with the vision of their founder Danny Thomas, no child is denied treatment based on race, religion or a familys ability to pay.'),(8820,392,'_builder_0_thumbnail_icontent_sections_2_content','field_6387822bdd583'),(8821,392,'builder_0_thumbnail_icontent_sections_3_thumbnail','292'),(8822,392,'_builder_0_thumbnail_icontent_sections_3_thumbnail','field_63878221dd582'),(8823,392,'builder_0_thumbnail_icontent_sections_3_content','<h2>FEED THE CHILDREN</h2>\r\nFeed the Children is dedicated to helping families and communities achieve stable lives and reduce the need for help tomorrow while providing the food and assistance they need today. In the United States, they distribute product donations of food and other items from corporate donors through a network of local community partners, provide classroom support and school supplies to students in vulnerable areas, and mobilize resources quickly to aid recovery efforts when natural disasters strike.'),(8824,392,'_builder_0_thumbnail_icontent_sections_3_content','field_6387822bdd583'),(8825,392,'builder_0_thumbnail_icontent_sections','4'),(8826,392,'_builder_0_thumbnail_icontent_sections','field_63878212dd581'),(8827,392,'builder_0_thumbnail_icontent',''),(8828,392,'_builder_0_thumbnail_icontent','field_63878194dd57d'),(8829,392,'builder_0_thumbnail_content_background_image',''),(8830,392,'_builder_0_thumbnail_content_background_image','field_638781c0dd57e'),(8831,392,'builder_0_thumbnail_content_style',''),(8832,392,'_builder_0_thumbnail_content_style','field_638781f8dd57f'),(8833,392,'builder_0_thumbnail_content_classes',''),(8834,392,'_builder_0_thumbnail_content_classes','field_63878207dd580'),(8835,392,'builder_0_thumbnail_content_sections_0_thumbnail','289'),(8836,392,'_builder_0_thumbnail_content_sections_0_thumbnail','field_63878221dd582'),(8837,392,'builder_0_thumbnail_content_sections_0_content','Tunnel to Towers Foundation has been helping Americas heroes since 9/11 by providing mortgage-free homes to Gold Star and fallen first responder families with young children and by building custom-designed smart homes for catastrophically injured veterans and first responders. They are also committed to eradicating veteran homelessness and aiding the victims of major U.S. disasters.'),(8838,392,'_builder_0_thumbnail_content_sections_0_content','field_6387822bdd583'),(8839,392,'builder_0_thumbnail_content_sections_1_thumbnail','290'),(8840,392,'_builder_0_thumbnail_content_sections_1_thumbnail','field_63878221dd582'),(8841,392,'builder_0_thumbnail_content_sections_1_content','Homes For Our Troops builds and donates specially adapted custom homes nationwide for severely injured post-9/11 Veterans, to enable them to rebuild their lives. Most of these Veterans have sustained injuries including multiple limb amputations, partial or full paralysis, and/or severe traumatic brain injury (TBI). These homes restore some of the freedom and inde