ence of the property acquisitions at American Postal Infrastructure Partners. She provides direct support to our clients and sellers, and other parties to the transaction. She works closely with third party vendors, attorneys, and lenders to seamlessly bring contracts to a close. She establishes strong relationships and creates a partnership to insure a smooth closing transaction. Christina brings over 20 years experience in real estate transactions specializing in land title. She started her career as a Paralegal overseeing real estate transactions from contract to closing, with an emphasis on curative and due diligence items. Christina has spent over 15 years in the title insurance industry as a Sr. Title Examiner and RE Paralegal. Having managed teams and being on all sides of the real estate transaction over two decades she brings extensive experience in title insurance, land title, underwriting and risk management. Christina is a Certified Paralegal, earning her degree from MacCormac College, Chicago, focusing on Real Estate Law. She has also earned both her Illinois Title Professional (ITP) and Illinois Escrow Professional (IEP) designation. Christina is an avid traveler and enjoys spending time with family and friends.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #2b449c;\">CP: MacCormac College</span>'),(9302,400,'_builder_0_team_sections_1_team_member_0_content','field_6387a70bfcf9c'),(9303,400,'builder_0_team_sections_1_team_member_1_headshot','361'),(9304,400,'_builder_0_team_sections_1_team_member_1_headshot','field_6387a8658d719'),(9305,400,'builder_0_team_sections_1_team_member_1_name','Shawn Gibbons'),(9306,400,'_builder_0_team_sections_1_team_member_1_name','field_6387a6fdfcf9a'),(9307,400,'builder_0_team_sections_1_team_member_1_title','Vice President of Acquisitions'),(9308,400,'_builder_0_team_sections_1_team_member_1_title','field_6387a703fcf9b'),(9309,400,'builder_0_team_sections_1_team_member_1_email','sgibbons@american-postal.com'),(9310,400,'_builder_0