sName\":\"text-accent-secondary h2\"} -->\n<p class=\"text-accent-secondary h2\">American Postal Infrastructure was established with the mission of maintaining and revitalizing the critical last-mile delivery infrastructure to support American communities. Just as important, our commitment to ESG is a key part of our mission. As an example, it is part of our policy to make sure all underground storage tanks (USTs) are removed before we close on properties to ensure our locations are a model of sustainability. We have removed over 12 USTs.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:shortcode -->\n[button href=\"#\" class=\"btn-main\" style=\"\"]<span class=\"light\">We offer two main options to owners.</span><br>LEARN MORE[/button]\n<!-- /wp:shortcode -->','Environmental Social Governance','','publish','closed','closed','','environmental-social-governance','','','2022-11-30 18:37:17','2022-11-30 18:37:17','',0,'http://localhost:8888/americanpostal/?page_id=46',0,'page','',0),(47,1,'2022-11-23 20:11:59','2022-11-23 20:11:59','','Environmental Social Governance','','inherit','closed','closed','','46-revision-v1','','','2022-11-23 20:11:59','2022-11-23 20:11:59','',46,'http://localhost:8888/americanpostal/?p=47',0,'revision','',0),(48,1,'2022-11-23 20:12:13','2022-11-23 20:12:13','<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1>OUR <strong>SPONSORS</strong></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"className\":\"text-accent-secondary h2\"} -->\n<p class=\"text-accent-secondary h2\">Our API team truly cares about people and our communities. We are dedicated to making a positive impact on the communities we serve and have partnered with a select group of organizations that support First Responders, Veterans, Childrens Hospitals, and Hunger Relief. We are honored to announce our support of Tunnel to Towers Foundation, Homes For Our Troops, St. Jude Childrens Research Hospital, and Feed the Children. We invite all postal owners to choose one of these charities when selling thei